基督教民主党提名Carlos Rivas Zamora和Merlin Peña为总统竞选搭档，但在2009年2月2日退出选举。<ref>{{cite news |title=Christian Dems Quit Salvador Election Race |url=http://www.plenglish.com/article.asp?ID={61FD8272-885A-4BBB-A4D8-C0EA32EB4D65})&language=EN |work=[[Prensa_Latina|Prensa Latina]] |date=3 February 2009 |accessdate=11 March 2009 }}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>其他政党的总统候选人退出竞选后，只剩FMLN和ARENA两个政党。

==选举结果==
FMLN以51.3%的选票赢得选举，ARENA获得48.7%，失去连续20年的执政党资格。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7944899.stm|title=Left-winger wins El Salvador poll|date=2009-03-16|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2009-03-17|archive-date=2010-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122004910/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7944899.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>获胜后富内斯说，“这是我一生中最高兴的夜晚，我想让它成为萨尔瓦多最具希望的一个夜晚。我想感谢所有投票支持我和选择希望与改革之路的人们，”新总统说，“相信希望和克服恐惧的人们今天已经获胜，这是全体萨尔瓦多人的胜利。”<ref name="WP">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/03/16/AR2009031600038.html|title=Leftist Declares Victory In El Salvador Election|last=Booth|first=William|date=2009-03-16|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=2009-03-17|archive-date=2019-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191014085321/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/03/16/AR2009031600038.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>罗德里戈·阿维拉在现任总统埃利亚斯·萨卡陪同下，承认失败并祝福富内斯“好运”。<ref name="WP"/> 

各国政府称将会与新政府展开合作，包括[[台湾|台湾]]和[[美国|美国]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/asiapacific/news/article_1465047.php/Taiwan_to_strengthen_ties_with_El_Salvadors_next_president_ |accessdate=2009-03-17 |title=Taiwan to strengthen ties with El Salvador's next president |date=2009-03-16 |publisher=M&C |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090319181843/http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/asiapacific/news/article_1465047.php/Taiwan_to_strengthen_ties_with_El_Salvadors_next_president_ |archivedate=2009-03-19 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jqH60lqIx63fXwtnwkeoWRZNMjdQ|title=US congratulates leftist winner in El Salvador|date=2009-03-16|publisher=AFP|accessdate=2009-03-17|archive-date=2012-07-31|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120731191747/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5jqH60lqIx63fXwtnwkeoWRZNMjdQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>面对外界对萨尔瓦多与美国关系下一步走向的猜测，富内斯15日说：“与拉丁美洲的一体化以及加强与美国的关系将是我们对外政策中优先考虑的方面。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.china.com.cn/international/txt/2009-03/17/content_17454045.htm|title=萨尔瓦多反对党候选人赢得总统选举|date=2009-03-16|publisher=路透社|accessdate=2014-04-28|archive-date=2018-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928170827/http://www.china.com.cn/international/txt/2009-03/17/content_17454045.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

